3. Pet:snake is somewhere to the right of Beverage:juice##5
4. Pet:goat is on the left of Pet:snake##1
5. Beverage:juice is between Beverage:7up and Beverage:sprite##2

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1     |     2      |       3       |    4    |
| Pet     | hedgehog | goat       | snake         | dog     |
| Beverage   | sprite   | juice | 7up | soy-milk |

