.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-4::.
Hobby: collecting, traveling, woodworking, writing
Pet: frog, guinea-pig, fish, goldfish
1. Pet:goldfish is on the far left or far right##3
2. Hobby:collecting is somewhere between Pet:guinea-pig and Hobby:writing##7
3. Hobby:woodworking == Pet:goldfish##1
4. Pet:fish is on the left of Pet:goldfish##1
5. Hobby:traveling is on the left of Pet:frog##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1     |     2      |       3       |      4      |
| Hobby   | traveling | collecting | writing       | woodworking |
| Pet   | guinea-pig      | frog   | fish | goldfish  |

