2. Movie-Genre:satire != Birthday:october##6
3. Birthday:july != Movie-Genre:thriller##6
4. Movie-Genre:thriller is somewhere to the right of Birthday:june##5
5. Movie-Genre:family == Birthday:april##1
6. Movie-Genre:western is somewhere to the right of Birthday:april##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2    |   3    |    4     |
| Movie-Genre   | family | western | satire | thriller |
| Birthday           | april    | july   | june  | october      |

